        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'In M365 Copilot (m365.cloud.microsoft) > left nav > Agents > Cowork. Send ONE prompt that delegates 5 parallel sub-tasks: "Cowork, prepare my 5-day Komite kit on the 38% attrition and renewal pressure. In parallel: (1) draft a 2-page Komite briefing memo as Komite_Briefing_Attrition_SLA.docx using /BPO_01_Service_Delivery.xlsx and /BPO_06_Renewal_Pipeline.xlsx; (2) draft a 1-page anchor client holding statement as Client_Holding_Line.docx using /BPO_02_Client_Service_Agreement.docx; (3) send an email to the 4 amber anchor clients using the holding statement as the body, subject \'Update on Q4 Service Delivery and FY2026 Commitment\'; (4) schedule a 60-minute Teams meeting for the Komite Eksekutif and the COO titled \'Pre-Komite Workforce & SLA Walkthrough\' for tomorrow 10:00 with the briefing memo attached; (5) post a Teams message in the Operations and Client Success channels that the Komite pack is being assembled, with attached briefing. Report back when each task is complete." Cowork executes all 5 in parallel and returns a status table.'},
