        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'In M365 Copilot > Agents > Cowork. Send ONE prompt that delegates 5 parallel sub-tasks: "Cowork, prepare my OJK and lender alignment package after the Board pre-read. In parallel: (1) draft a 1-page lender briefing as Lender_Briefing_Capex.docx using /TC_06_Capex_Approvals_Tracker.xlsx and /TC_01_Network_Performance.xlsx; (2) draft a 1-page OJK note as OJK_Note_Digital_Payments.docx using /TC_05_Kominfo_BRTI_Submissions.docx and /TC_02_Spectrum_Compliance_Report.docx; (3) send an email to the lead relationship bank using the lender briefing as the body, subject \'FY2026 Capex Envelope and Spectrum Compliance\'; (4) schedule a 45-minute Teams meeting for the CFO, Treasurer, and Regulatory Affairs titled \'Lender & OJK Pre-Brief\' for the day after the Board meeting at 14:00; (5) post a Teams message in the Finance and Regulatory channels that the briefings are in flight and require sign-off by EOD. Report back."'}
